      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, honest condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor door dings, and thinning clear coat on the hood, while the interior displays typical wear on the driver's seat and some fading on the dashboard plastics. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, though it will likely need suspension bushings and new tires in the near future. It is a solid, functional option for a buyer who doesn't mind a bit of character and is looking for a dependable powertrain at a reasonable price point.",
