    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this absolute beauty in person! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've taken obsessive care of it, so you won't find a single scratch or dent anywhere. It drives like a total dream\u2014super smooth and responsive. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one! Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re going to love it!",
