    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black Metallic. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is routed through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally optimized with a proactive subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement (VAC coated), a comprehensive VANOS overhaul (Beisan systems), and a valve clearance adjustment. The suspension retains its factory-correct MacPherson strut and multi-link geometry, providing unparalleled feedback. This is a zero-fault, concours-level driver's car with impeccable paint depth and a pristine interior.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
