    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is a true collector-grade example that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior retains its deep, factory-original luster with zero swirl marks or rock chips, while the interior still carries that new-car aroma with absolutely no bolster wear, carpet staining, or sun fading on the dash. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions flawlessly, and the engine bay is immaculate, showing no signs of fluid seepage or corrosion. It comes with a complete, documented service history, both original master keys, and all factory manuals. This car represents a rare opportunity to own a specimen that drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
